<p class="apache">Apache HTTP Sunucusu S&uuml;r&uuml;m 2.4</p>
<img alt="" src="../images/feather.png"></div>
<div class="up"><a href="./"><img title="<-" alt="<-" src="../images/left.gif"></a></div>
<div id="path">
<a href="https://www.apache.org/">Apache</a> &gt; <a href="https://httpd.apache.org/">HTTP Sunucusu</a> &gt; <a href="https://httpd.apache.org/docs/">Belgeleme</a> &gt; <a href="../">S&uuml;r&uuml;m 2.4</a> &gt; <a href="./">&Ccedil;eşitli Belgeler</a></div><div id="page-content"><div id="preamble"><h1>Apache'de Başarımın Arttırılması</h1>
